\id 3JN  
\ide UTF-8
\h 3 Joni 
\toc1 3 Joni 
\toc2 3 Joni 
\toc3 3jn 
\mt1 3 Joni  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Mupati kuli uyandika Gayiyasi, ooyo ngwenjanda chakasimpe.  
\v 2 Oyandwa, Ndikukkombela ikuti zintu zyoonse zikwendele kabotu alubo upone kabotu, mbuli mbopona kabotu mumuuya wako.  
\v 3 Nkambo ndakakondwa ndakabotelwa loko inzubo nizyakasika akupa bukamboni bwakasimpe kaako, mbuli mboyenda mukasimpe.  
\v 4 Nsikwe kubotelwa kumbi kwinda oku pe, ikumvwa kuti bana bangu benda mukasimpe.  
\v 5 Oyandwa, uchita michito chalusyomo mpobelekela inzubo akubenzu,  
\v 6 aabo bakazopa bukamboni bwaluyando lwako kunembo lyembungano. Uchita kabotu kubasindikila munyeendo zyabo chakubotezya Leza,  
\v 7 nkambo kezina eelyo ndibayobwendela, nkabata tambwide chintu kuli bamasi.  
\v 8 Aboobo aswebo tulachitambula mbubo, ikuti tukabe basimulimo nyokwe mukasimpe.  
\v 9 Kuli nzindakalembela imbungano, pesi Diyotilefesi, oyo uyandisya kuba mutanzi akati kabo, tatutambuli pe swebo.  
\v 10 Eelyo, nindasika, nzomuyeezya milimo yakwe njali kuchita, yakututamikizya chakubeja amajwi mabi kulindiswe. Mukutakkutisika, takaki biyo kutambula ibana bakwabo, pesi ulakasya alubo kulaabo ibayanda kubatambula benzu mpawo akubatanda mumbungano.  
\v 11 Noyandwa, utatobeli kuchita zibi pesi kuleezyo zibotu. Ooyo uchita zibotu nguwa Leza; simuchita zibi tanakubona Leza,  
\v 12 Demetiliyasi wakatambula bukamboni bubotu kuli boonse amukasimpe. Alubo andiswe tuli bakamboni, alubo ayebo ulizi kuti bukamboni bwesu mbwakasimpe.  
\v 13 Ndali ezyiingi zyakukulembela pesi nsikkonzyi kukulembela pe zyoonse empesele amulende.  
\v 14 Pesi ndilangila kuzokubona lino lino, elyo tuzowambuula katulangene.  
\v 15 Lumuno alube ayebo. Benzuma balikumujuzya. Ujuzye ibeenzuma oko muzina.   